     "transition_in": "blur", "transition_text": "THE FIVE DOORS...",
     "vo": "So here they are. Door one, your Google profile and the map, that little pack at the top of the search. Door two, your website. Door three, paid ads. Door four, lead networks, the apps like Angi and Thumbtack. And door five, your reviews and word of mouth.",
     "assets": [{"id": "phonemap", "w": 190, "x": 300, "y": 640, "anim": "drawOn", "t": 0.6, "label": "GOOGLE"},
                {"id": "laptop", "w": 220, "x": 640, "y": 640, "anim": "popIn", "t": 4.2, "sfx": "pop", "label": "WEBSITE"},
                {"id": "megaphone", "w": 200, "x": 960, "y": 640, "anim": "popIn", "t": 6.0, "sfx": "pop", "label": "PAID ADS"},
                {"id": "leadapp", "w": 190, "x": 1290, "y": 640, "anim": "popIn", "t": 8.0, "sfx": "ping", "label": "LEAD APPS"},
                {"id": "reviewstars", "w": 230, "x": 1620, "y": 640, "anim": "popIn", "t": 11.0, "sfx": "ding", "label": "REVIEWS"}]},
    {"id": "everyone", "text": "EVERY CUSTOMER WALKS ONE", "text_y": 110, "emph": "ONE",
     "vo": "Every single customer you will ever book walks through one of those five. Memorize them.",
     "assets": [{"id": "person", "w": 150, "x": 660, "y": 620, "anim": "drawOn", "t": 0.4, "label": "A CUSTOMER"},
                {"id": "door", "w": 240, "x": 1280, "y": 640, "anim": "popIn", "t": 2.2, "sfx": "thunk"}]},
