    {"id": "backwards", "text": "DON'T START WITH THE ROOF", "text_y": 110, "emph": "ROOF", "mood": "frustrated",
     "vo": "And here's where most guys screw it up. They ignore the free doors, the ones that actually compound over time, and dump their whole budget into the paid ones. That's building your house starting with the roof.",
     "char": {"x": 320, "y": 460, "scale": 0.58, "hat": "hardhat"},
