     "transition_in": "blur", "transition_text": "A HEALTHY MIX...",
     "vo": "A healthy contractor doesn't live behind one door. Picture a pie. Maybe forty percent of your work comes from paid, ads and lead apps. Thirty percent from Google and your website.",
