                {"id": "phonemap", "w": 170, "x": 1520, "y": 600, "anim": "popIn", "t": 6.0, "sfx": "ping", "label": "30% GOOGLE"}]},
    {"id": "referralgold", "text": "REFERRALS = GOLD", "text_y": 120, "emph": "GOLD",
     "vo": "Twenty percent from referrals and repeat customers, the gold. And ten percent from everything else. No single door owns you. That's a business that sleeps at night.",
