                {"id": "megaphone", "w": 220, "x": 1440, "y": 600, "anim": "popIn", "t": 5.4, "sfx": "pop", "label": "ADS"}]},
    {"id": "projects", "text": "BIG PROJECTS → REVIEWS", "text_y": 115, "emph": "REVIEWS",
     "vo": "Bigger project work, roofing, remodels, a new system, that leans harder on reviews and a real website, because folks research before they spend big. Same five doors. Different weight.",
